<plot>Imprisoned for a crime she didn't commit, Alexandra entrusts the care of Rebecca into the hands of her best friend, Kelly.While in prison, Alexandra fights to survive the trauma of the separation from her daughter. She must learn to stand up for herself if she ever has hopes of seeing Rebecca again. After a year of incarceration and many futile calls and letters, Kelly reluctantly brings Rebecca to visit her mother. Disgusted with Alexandra's imprisonment, Kelly never returns, keeping Rebecca from Alexandra.Two years later, Alexandra is released on account of her good behavior and is now on her way to reclaim her daughter...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?074904</url></doc>
